  carrier := ⋃ N, ⋃ hN, B N hN
  sSupIndep' x hx a ha ha' := by
    sorry
  sSup_eq_top' := by
    sorry
  not_bot_mem' := by simp [Set.mem_iUnion, hB'']
```

So, the refinement is defined as the set of all submodules `p` such that `p ∈ B N hN` for some `N ∈ D` and `hN`. So, the carrier is `⋃ N, ⋃ hN, B N hN`. 

